{"tid":795921,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"🌟日本兔兔島: 大久野島🐰😊+兔仔傷心 憂愁【身體語言】","createTime":"2018-08-27T11:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T03:51:11.000Z","uid":197098,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"923696110d76cc17c58e384d61f53dcac4b4f0be","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"大家有沒有去過日本「兔兔島」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e466aff5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a><br />\n<br />\n但是其實島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等等，給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食, 例如：蘿蔔和水果。當兔子有一隻耳向前、一隻耳向後或一隻耳向上、一隻耳垂下，即代表牠有一點不開心或一點憤怒。但當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=03d29f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a> <br />\n<br />\n另一個video 看到兔子憂愁, 耳朵越後就越不開心。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=3f0e1114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a> <br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來 。<br />\n以下video 也是另一個例子，兔子生病(痙攣):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=85644973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">N.B.</span>: 實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會參觀然後領養，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=596a0bc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"81a37a07583bfbaa924bb8cde509663fc36a6763","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"更多關於兔仔憂愁的身體語言：<a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=49b35444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a>"},{"pid":"33aeb251e62273a54cd757ae8047ba6d18f3940e","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:41:03.000Z","msg":"兔洞穴究竟有幾深？🐰<br />\n<br />\n原來洞穴內還可以分隔「房間」給每隻兔子😱😊<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/62vSzCsR1Zs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F62vSzCsR1Zs&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=21f9de3d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/62vSzCsR1Zs</a>"},{"pid":"efbd52a527395c04afd17918df6aad15bf47dd31","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T14:16:46.000Z","msg":"🌟兔兔打籃球打到累了, 然後睡了😆😊🐰<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrQcoSxQj95s&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=76d7b185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rQcoSxQj95s</a>"},{"pid":"78d03e159c64d028659b8b6b8ecc02c378dc3077","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。兔子在室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有任何天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。以下2個videos 可以看到兔子最開心的時候：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5b130759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFDMWC5U0gkw&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=98a4f499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FDMWC5U0gkw</a>"},{"pid":"bcf05ba100a893ea553beb60d50e892319d56a01","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"兔子的鼻子移動時代表當時專注，可以因為牠對某事物感興趣或好奇，移動得越快就越專注。但鼻子移動亦可以代表焦慮，要看當時的情況。通常兔子感到輕鬆時牠們鼻子會移動。<br />\n<br />\n你可以做一個有趣的實驗(或可變成一個對話技巧)：趴在地上面向兔子，重複地把上唇卷入上牙下面來模仿兔子鼻子移動(如果有鬍子會更有效)，然後改變速度看看兔子的反應。移動速度首先比兔兔慢，然後加速，牠可能會因為專注程度增加而跟你加速，然後你再減慢，此時牠亦可能跟著減慢。牠亦可能會覺得迷惑。(最好做之前告訴家人以免覺得怪）<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到兔子鼻子移動：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8Tozjowr2JY&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=02d2aff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8Tozjowr2JY</a> <br />\n<br />\n更多關於兔子鼻子移動: <a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Ffollow-my-nose%2F&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=516dc21e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/follow-my-nose/</a>"},{"pid":"c26e95ed55eb2d8c461f786b23252841fd4fb56e","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:30:47.000Z","msg":"為什麼兔仔咬籠子？🐰🐰😊<br />\n<br />\n兔子咬籠其實是想引主人注意，覺得悶，告訴主人牠想出來玩和探索。兔子咬東西是自然的，牠們在大自然是用腳和牙齒來掘洞穴。由於牠們的牙齒不斷生長，咬東西可以幫牠們磨短。喜歡咬東西的兔子是聰明、親切、喜歡引人注意(或其他兔注意)。有時候主人正在整理東西，牠們過來其實想一起參與。除了提供無限Hay幫助牠們磨牙外，主人可以買一些草墊、草屋、cardboard給牠們咬。兔子喜歡吸引人注意，有時我們看電視的時候，兔子會躺在電視機前面，幸好牠們不知道我們其實不在看牠們。因此，經常陪牠們玩是重要的，兔子是群體性動物，如果主人沒有空，最好領養多一隻兔子陪伴牠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_GZZCdCLIKo&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=cdede57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_GZZCdCLIKo</a>"},{"pid":"a99a9953152f26224f861bf0488585a0d58152c8","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T11:26:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養了兔兔，改變了牠的生命！牠還會經常binky(跳兔子舞) ! <br />\n<br />\n(兔子binky是兔子最開心的狀態。當牠們binky 時，這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5754cb80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a></span>"},{"pid":"dede9299182ecba1d9ea250040c1e3f6a826cb3b","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"兔兔很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=632bd2b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a><br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過幫兔子洗澡，可能見過兔兔用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，兔子在3:26被嚇暈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=6e79bbee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a>"},{"pid":"25eff7cbcc25bc37289bfa9463830bd17b2e9d25","tid":795921,"uid":31788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"6月去完，好可愛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/205604_7c1ea37437ee8e8e24a9b61c7431a694.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F205604_7c1ea37437ee8e8e24a9b61c7431a694.png&h=5e33322d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b2321dced8804fcceda45ca3ac5f1049f2eb6ba","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25eff7cbcc25bc37289bfa9463830bd17b2e9d25","tid":795921,"uid":31788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"6月去完，好可愛<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/205604_7c1ea37437ee8e8e24a9b61c7431a694.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F205604_7c1ea37437ee8e8e24a9b61c7431a694.png&h=5e33322d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:02:03.000Z","msg":"6月氣候怎樣？"},{"pid":"b4501b843ff693d6012bf91abe0a21abcc607c47","tid":795921,"uid":6717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"應該好臭？"},{"pid":"63940023ffcd7b96f9bfb63f1f413559122f8a08","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"狗狗搶野食，兔兔毫無還擊之力!🙈🙈<br />\n<br />\n兔仔正前方是盲點，除了這盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。當牠們側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。大眼睛和大耳朵的構造讓牠們可以偵測到捕獵者(predatory animals)追食。牠們比我們人類看的顏色有限。(你可想像正前方是盲點，側面才看得最清楚，前腳移動有限，又怎會攻擊到他人？）兔子在主人面前會以有限的視角，靈敏的嗅覺、聽覺和觸覺去偵測主人。兔子也有遠視，所以在牠們的視線範圍內走得越遠，牠們就看得越清楚。 以下video 可看到狗狗搶吃兔糧, 兔兔毫無還擊之力：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJKwW65LcLIg&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=40b28cf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JKwW65LcLIg</a> <br />\nhahaha"},{"pid":"b212b9b00669168c68725cff950c696fafb93951","tid":795921,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"這隻兔兔的睡覺姿態很可愛！🐰🌟<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sHAXSvTAXoU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsHAXSvTAXoU&d=C53iIvXIKURM8r9PQdp7%2BMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ebc0583f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sHAXSvTAXoU</a>"}]}